# ActionSheetFinder 
A useful utility for plugin developers to figure out what ActionSheet you pressed. Will output as a Toast and additionally will show up in the Debug Logs.

Download: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/byeoon/ActionSheetFinder/main/dist/ActionSheetFinder.js
Source: https://github.com/byeoon/ActionSheetFinder
